Oheneba bụ ọkwa eze a na-enye nwa nwanyị ma ọ bụ nwa nwoke nke eze ma ọ bụ onyeisi
Ọ bụ ihe yiri nwa eze ma ọ bụ nwa eze nwanyị (site na Latin princeps, nke pụtara nwa amaala)
Ọtụtụ mgbe, a na-eji okwu ahụ eme ihe maka nwa eze, ma ọ bụ maka nwa nwanyị eze.
Okwu Twi sitere, site na okwu Twi na akan ohene, nke pụtara "onye isi ma ọ bụ eze" na ''ba' kwa site na okwu twi na akan, nke pụtara nwa, na abụọ pụtara 'nwa onye isi' ma ọ bụ 'nwa eze'.
N'ọdịnala Akan na ọchịchị Akan, nwa nke eze ma ọ bụ onye isi anaghị arịgoro n'ocheeze mgbe nna ya nwụrụ n'ihi ihe nketa nke Matrilineal na nchichi ha
Otú ọ dị, a na-enye ụmụaka aha Oheneba nke pụtara "Nwa onyeisi" ma ọ bụ "Nwa eze"
A na-echekwa aha ahụ ọbụna mgbe ndị nna ha (eze) gafere.
